'''Vrortic cocktail''' was a [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] dish that combined various meats and layers of [[Wroshyr tree/Legends|wroshyr leaves]] that had been soaked in potent [[Grakkyn]] nectar for weeks. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] deemed it as a "safe" food, fit for [[Human/Legends|Human]] consumption&mdash;as many Wookiee foods were spicy enough to cause damage to a Human's gullet.

